## Adding New Lessons

After any user correction or debugging insight:
1. Add a new section with clear title
2. Include context, what happened, and solution
3. Note which files or patterns it applies to
4. Keep entries concise (3–5 lines each)

Aim for 5–15 entries max; delete obsolete ones.
